          "Sometimes, there‚Äôs just not a lot of great information to show for a search, or the results are changing quickly ‚Äì and it‚Äôs important to have that context. To address these information gaps, Search will automatically show content advisories in situations when a topic is rapidly evolving, or when our systems don‚Äôt have high confidence in the overall quality of the results available for the search."
